snippet.title: Steam Next Fest June 2022 Live Stream of World Turtles
snippet.description:
World Turtles recently participated in the Steam Next Fest of 13-20 June 2022. This was one of the live streams I did, in which everything in the game worked well, right up to helicopters, water ways and additional Founders Hex.

Free Demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1512050/World_Turtles/

Discord Server:
https://discord.com/invite/2NEb4HxwhF

Mini Trailer
https://youtu.be/RplL7hp1-L4

Subreddit:
https://www.reddit.com/r/World_Turtles/
